      • display_header_footer

        public boolean display_header_footer
        Set to true to print headers and footers or false to not print headers and footers. Modify header_template and/or footer_template to customize the display.(设置为true可打印页眉和页脚，设置为false可不打印页眉和脚注。修改header_template和/或footer_template以自定义显示。)

      • footer_template

        public java.lang.String footer_template
        HTML template for the print footer. Only displayed if |display_header_footer| is true (1). Uses the same format as |header_template|.(打印页脚的HTML模板。仅当|display_header_footer|为true（1）时显示。使用与|header_template|相同的格式。)

      • generate_document_outline

      • header_template

        public java.lang.String header_template
        HTML template for the print header. Only displayed if |display_header_footer| is true (1). Should be valid HTML markup with the following classes used to inject printing values into them: - date: formatted print date - title: document title - url: document location - pageNumber: current page number - totalPages: total pages in the document For example, "" would generate a span containing the title.(打印头的HTML模板。仅当|display_header_footer|为true（1）时显示。应该是有效的HTML标记，并使用以下类将打印值注入其中：-date:格式化的打印日期 -title:文档标题 -url:文档位置 -pageNumber:当前页码 -totalPages:文档中的总页数。例如，“”将生成包含标题的跨度。)

      • page_ranges

        public java.lang.String page_ranges
        Paper ranges to print, one based, e.g., '1-5, 8, 11-13'. Pages are printed in the document order, not in the order specified, and no more than once. Defaults to empty string, which implies the entire document is printed. The page numbers are quietly capped to actual page count of the document, and ranges beyond the end of the document are ignored. If this results in no pages to print, an error is reported. It is an error to specify a range with start greater than end.(要打印的纸张范围，基于一个范围，例如“1-5、8、11-13”。页面按文档顺序打印，而不是按指定的顺序打印，并且打印次数不得超过一次。默认为空字符串，这意味着打印整个文档。页码以文档的实际页数为上限，并且忽略文档末尾以外的范围。如果这导致没有要打印的页面，则会报告错误。指定起始大于结束的范围是错误的。)

      • paper_height

        public double paper_height

      • paper_width

        public double paper_width
        Output paper size in inches. If either of these values is less than or equal to zero then the default paper size (letter, 8.5 x 11 inches) will be used.(输出纸张大小（以英寸为单位）。如果这些值中的任何一个小于或等于零，则将使用默认纸张大小（字母，8.5 x 11英寸）。)

      • prefer_css_page_size

        public boolean prefer_css_page_size
        Set to true to prefer page size as defined by css. Defaults to false in which case the content will be scaled to fit the paper size.(设置为true可首选css定义的页面大小。默认值为false，在这种情况下，内容将按比例缩放以适应纸张大小。)

      • print_background

        public boolean print_background
        Set to true to print background graphics or false to not print background graphics.(设置为true可打印背景图形，设置为false可不打印背景图形。)

      • scale

        public double scale
        The percentage to scale the PDF by before printing (e.g. .5 is 50%). If this value is less than or equal to zero the default value of 1.0 will be used.(打印前按比例缩放PDF的百分比（例如，.5为50%）。如果该值小于或等于零，则将使用默认值1.0。)
